From: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Date: Wed, 9 Feb 2022 09:28:23 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] scsi: drbd: Remove WRITE_SAME support
Git-commit: a34592ff6b78e84e11b19183b60cd240737f76f9
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1183

REQ_OP_WRITE_SAME was only ever submitted by the legacy Linux zeroing code,
which has switched to use REQ_OP_WRITE_ZEROES long ago.

